<div1 facs="#zone_wdy_qpm_3jb" type="EMIN">
<p>
<lb/>Vech-i tahrīr-i hurūf oldur ki
					<lb/>işbu <date type="created" when="1790-09-08" when-custom="1204">bin iki yüz dört senesinde</date> der ʿuhde ve iltizā-
					<lb/>mımızda bulunan <placeName corresp="#Kirşevo">Kirşevo</placeName> mukātaʿası kurālarında
					<lb/><placeName corresp="#KYSN" facs="#zone_xlv_dvb_qqb">KOYSINA</placeName> karyesi hudūd dāhilinde arāz[ī]-ı mīrīye-
					<lb/>si mutasarrıflarında <persName corresp="#mutasarrıf_YUZB" facs="#zone_jxr_vvb_qqb">zimmī YUZB veled-i Nikola YÖRK</persName>
<lb/>nām zimmīnin kendi taht-ı tasarrıfında bir kıtʿa tarla ...
					<lb/><placeName corresp="#LOÇÇE" facs="#zone_cwm_3wb_qqb">LOÇÇE</placeName> demekle hudūd ... -sıyla işbu dārende-i hurūf
					<lb/><placeName corresp="#Kirşevo">Kirşevo</placeName> kilisanın gardiyān <persName corresp="#gardiyān_Marko" facs="#zone_rgt_dxb_qqb">HRA Marko KRAKİÇ</persName>
<lb/>nām zimmīnin resmiyle on beş asadī guruş mukābele-
					<lb/>sinde beyʿ ve ferāğ edüp onlar dahi kabūl edüb
					<lb/>biz dahi me'mūrimiz ... cāiz
					<lb/>görüp tasarrıfına kimesne māniʿ olunmaya
				</p>
<div2 facs="#zone_wry_spm_3jb" type="sign">
<p>
<lb/><persName corresp="#emīn_Ahmed">El-fakīr
						<lb/>Ahmed Emīn-i
						<lb/><placeName>Kirşevo</placeName></persName>
</p>
</div2>
<div2 type="şühūdu'l-hāl">
<p>
<lb/>Şühūdu'l-hāl
						<lb/><persName facs="#zone_ecx_p53_qqb">Mollā(?) Sālih
						<lb/>Paşalık ʿan
						<lb/>Müslimīn<persName/>
<lb/><persName facs="#zone_o5p_t53_qqb">Sālih ʿAlemdār(?)
								<lb/>GOGAzāde</persName>
<lb/><persName facs="#zone_wfs_nv3_qqb">Zimmī Mato LALK</persName>
<lb/><persName facs="#zone_lz2_pv3_qqb">Zimmī PETRORAK</persName>
<lb/><persName facs="#zone_afj_qv3_qqb">Zimmī GAŞO KRAKK
								<lb/>ʿan VARNK</persName></persName>
</p>
<div2 type="note">
<p>
<lb/>Be-her nakit para ... </p>
</div2>
</div2>
<div1 facs="#zone_hcg_2qm_3jb" type="summary_Croatian">
<p>
<lb/>Die <date cert="low" type="summary_Croatian" when="1791-03-10">10 Mar(?) 1791</date>
<lb/>Kupi manashi od ...
					<lb/>mahu ...
					<lb/>ljednu ...
					<lb/>goporida ...
					<lb/>mo dovniki ...
					<lb/>sanla, u ...
					<lb/>Nno 1.
					<lb/><date type="summary_Croatian" when="1790-09-08" when-custom="1204">1204</date>. </p>
</div1>
</div1>
